Package org.vanted.addons.lmme.core

Class LMMEController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vanted.addons.lmme.core.LMMEController
  • public class LMMEController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class controls and coordinates the actions of LMME.

    It implements the action listeners for the main button functions in the tab and maintains the available layout and decomposition algorithms.

    Author:
    Michael Aichem, Tobias Czauderna

      • setModelAction

        public void setModelAction()
        Implements the action for the 'Set Model' button in the Add-On tab.

        The currently selected SBML model is set as BaseGraph of the current session.

      • showOverviewGraphAction

        public void showOverviewGraphAction()
        Implements the action for the 'Show Overview Graph' button in the Add-On tab.

        Using the BaseGraph of the currentSession, the selected decomposition is performed and the overview graph is created and drawn according to the selected layout method..

      • showSubsystemGraphsAction

        public void showSubsystemGraphsAction()
        Implements the action for the 'Show Selected Subsystems' button in the Add-On tab.

        The selected subsystem nodes are read and the SubsystemGraph is constructed and laid out according to the selected layout method.

      • oraAction

        public void oraAction​(java.lang.String pathToDifferentiallyExpressedFile,
                      java.lang.String pathToReferenceFile)
               throws java.io.IOException
        Implements the action for the 'Over-Representation Analysis' button in the Add-On tab.

        The Over-Representation Analysis is performed and the results are highlighted in the overview graph.

        Parameters:
        pathToDifferentiallyExpressedFile - the path to the differentially expressed metabolites file in the local file system
        pathToReferenceFile - the path to the reference metabolites file in the local file system, may be null
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException

      • transformToSbgnAction

        public void transformToSbgnAction()
        Implements the action for the 'Translate to SBGN' button in the Add-On tab.

        Translates the representation of the SubsystemGraph to SBGN if the SBGN-ED add-on is available.

      • partiallyResetSession

        public void partiallyResetSession()
        Partially resets the session.

        The session is reseted, except that the selected model is kept and a new, clean BaseGraph is constructed from the latter.
